This was a birthday gift my daughter picked out for her friend.  Dolphin Tale was the main attraction but they were just as excited to watch the classics, Flipper and a Free Willy.
This is a very sweet film for kids.  I have a special needs child so the topic is especially endearing for my family.

If you know a kid that is going through a rough time dealing with being handicap, rare disease, disorder, or whatever these are all 3 perfect movies that boost their hopes and inspire them.  I know bc it did with our son who was diagnosed with a bone disease perthes.  And our 9yr old daughter LOVES em too!

This was a great deal to get 3 movies for less than I would normally pay for just 1.  It came on time as promised and was like brand new.

My little girl wanted to see Dolphin Tale 2 so I decided to get this to get an idea about the movie. The fact that it came with 2 more DVDs was a bonus. My daughter found the movie fascinating. She's watched it 3 times so far(since yesterday). She didn't care much about Flipper and we have not gotten to Free Willy yet. For the price, it's worth buying.
It arrived on time.  Item was as described. Item was packaged appropriately.  And we love it.
Great deal but would prefer if there were three different holders for the DVDs inside the case rather than having to stack them on top of one another.

Love the Dolphin Tale movie. However, the Free Willy version was a much older version than the one we have seen. We couldn't finish the movie. We tried to watch Flipper, but my daughter lost interest with it not even halfway in.

We bought this because my Daughter, age 9, wanted to see the first Dolphin Tale before going to see Dolphin Tale 2.  It was cheaper to buy this 3 for 1 than just Dolphin Tale alone!  She keeps watching Dolphin Tale over and over and likes it so much she hasn't even started the other 2 movies yet!  So I guess that means she likes it!

I grew up watching Chuck Conners as the "Rifleman", and that show was always about family values and morality.
These three movies fill that same space in my heart!
